SUMMARY:Complimentary Tickets to TIFF Oscar Watch Party + Trivia Show (St.
  Andrew Stn.)
DESCRIPTION:Experience Toronto\n**Note: There are 4 complimentary balcony 
 tickets together for 4 Experience Toronto Members who have attended at lea
 st 2 events. This event will not be hosted and members will meet outside A
 uditorium 1 to go in together.**\n\nOn **Sunday March 15th\,** be part of 
 the **The 98th Academy Awards Oscar Watch Party and Toronto Trivia Show at
  TIFF Bell Lightbox.** Join members at TIFF Lightbox for a special Oscars 
 Watch Party\, hosted by comedian Alice Rose! Celebrate Hollywood’s bigge
 st night\, live on the big screen\, with your fellow film lovers. And get 
 ready: before the show\, there will be movie trivia from Toronto Trivia. *
 *Note**: **I have 4 complimentary tickets for 4 members who have attended 
 at least 2 events.**\n\n**BEST PICTURE NOMINEES**\nBugonia\nF1\nFrankenste
 in\nHamnet\nMarty Supreme\nOne Battle After Another\nThe Secret Agent\nSen
 timental Value\nSinners\nTrain Dreams\n\n**COST**\nFree: for TIFF Members 
 or 1 complimentary ticket each for 4 Experience Toronto members\n\nNote: I
  will be charged if you do not show up for the event\, and this $15 fee wi
 ll be passed on to you and will also impact future membership attendance.\
 n\n**SIGNING UP**\n\n* **Simply RSVP Yes with your email address\, and you
  will be added to the Waitlist. I will check your past attendance (No show
 s are ineligible) and move the eligible attendee to going.**\n* **OR If yo
 u already have your ticket for this sold out event\, post your set number\
 ,** and I will move you to attending\n* **RSVPs close three days prior.** 
 Any confirmed attendees who cancel or do not show will be required to etra
 nsfer to me TIFF's no show fee of $15 and future attendance will be impact
 ed.\n* Your ticket will be emailed to you the morning of the event\, and y
 ou must accept it as soon as possible.\n\n**MEETUP TIME**\n**Meet members 
 at 6:45pm**: **Outside Auditorium 1 inside TIFF Bell Lightbox at 350 King 
 St. W. to head inside together**\n\n**Show starts**: **7pm**\n\nEnjoy and 
 please post your comments in the event after!
