SUMMARY:Start Spring with Dim Sum at this Top Dim Sum Restaurant (Spadina 
 Ave.)
DESCRIPTION:Experience Toronto\n**On Sunday 22nd March\, start Spring with
  some yummy Dim Sum.** I have been going to this place for over 20 years\,
  and have shared with many meetup groups\, so hope you will join us. Rol S
 ans moved to it's new address almost 2 years ago\, and I am looking forwar
 d to this modern location with their endless all-day dim sum menu. Framed 
 pictures of their bestsellers (and also mine) are above. Note: This will b
 e a shared experience at the table.\n\n**COST**\nDim Sum: Cost + Tip + Tax
 es will be divided equally amongst attendees\n\nOrganizer Meetup fee: $5\n
 \n**SIGNING-UP**\n\n* RSVP Yes and the system will add you to the wait lis
 t\n* To secure your seat\, a $10 etransfer (includes $5 meetup fee) is req
 uired to hold a seat at the table. Attendees will receive $5 back at the e
 nd of dim sum - there are no refunds for cancellations or no shows.\n* Onc
 e you are on the waitlist\, I will message you my email for the etransfer.
 \n* Once the transfer is complete\, I will move you to attending.\n* A rem
 inder will be sent the night before with my cell and all meetup details. M
 ake sure you set up your communication settings to receive.\n\nRSVPs close
  2 days prior. Cancellations will result in a No Show and impact future at
 tendance.\n\n**MEETUP TIME**\n**Meet me at: 11:45am inside the front doors
  of Rol Sans at 388 Spadina Ave.** Please wait for me to arrive\, and do n
 ot sit on your own prior\, so we can get the table requested.\n\nLength: 1
  hour 45mins\n\nEnjoy and please post your Comments in the event after.
